    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The exterior is clean with only minor surface scratches and small rock chips consistent with regular use, while the interior remains in great shape with no tears or heavy stains. Mechanically, the car is sound, featuring a responsive engine and smooth shifting, though it will eventually need standard maintenance items like brake pads in the coming months. It\u2019s a reliable, attractive car that is ready for its next owner to drive home today.",
