    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this distinguished vehicle, a testament to consistent care and mechanical integrity. This model has undergone a comprehensive professional assessment to ensure it meets our exacting standards for performance and reliability. Featuring a well-preserved interior and a resilient powertrain, this automobile offers a superior driving experience for those who prioritize both quality and value. We invite you to experience the refined engineering and enduring appeal of this exceptional selection.",
      "price": 34900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
