    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable set of wheels that won\u2019t let you down? This beauty has been my pride and joy and is still running like a champ! It\u2019s been well-loved and kept in really nice shape, making it the perfect choice for someone who wants a solid, dependable ride without the brand-new price tag. I\u2019ve made sure to keep up with it so it\u2019s ready for its next adventure with you! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'm super happy to chat and show you around the car!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a 2008 BMW M3 (E92) powered by the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 engine. This naturally aspirated powerplant features individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing, delivering a linear power band up to an 8,400 RPM redline. The 6-speed manual gearbox offers precise gate engagement, paired with the M Variable Differential Lock for superior torque distribution during high-lateral-G cornering. The chassis remains composed with M-specific aluminum suspension components and a stiffened subframe, providing the communicative feedback expected of the E9X platform. Recent service includes a diagnostic scan of the throttle actuators and a cooling system pressure test to ensure thermal efficiency. This example represents a mechanically sound driver's car with its factory-tuned hydraulic steering rack intact and responsive.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained engine. Clean interior. Clean title. Runs well.",
      "price": 32000.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously cared-for 2018 BMW M240i, presented in Alpine White with a Black Dakota leather interior. This car has been driven with respect and maintains a very clean profile. The exterior paint holds a brilliant shine, with only minor road-pebble nicks on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side wheel. Inside, the cockpit remains in great shape; the dashboard is free of cracks, and the leather upholstery is firm, showing only minimal entry wear on the driver\u2019s bolster. All power options, dual-zone climate control, and the navigation system are fully operational. Under the hood, the B58 engine runs perfectly with no leaks or unusual noises. It has a documented service history, including a recent brake fluid flush and oil service performed less than 1,000 miles ago. The tires are in good health with plenty of miles left. This car represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer looking for a reliable, high-performance coupe that has been kept in consistent, ready-to-drive condition. Includes two sets of keys and a clean title.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies reliable performance and aesthetic integrity. This unit has undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for safety and mechanical excellence. Offering a balanced combination of sophistication and proven durability, it represents an exceptional acquisition for the discerning driver who values both quality and value. We invite you to experience the superior handling and refined interior that distinguish this particular model from its peers.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for your next adventure? I\u2019m parting with my car, and it\u2019s been such a fantastic companion on the road. It runs beautifully and has been well-maintained, so it\u2019s in really solid shape for its next owner! Whether you're commuting or heading out on a road trip, this car is super comfortable and a joy to drive. I'm looking for a quick, smooth sale, so feel free to reach out with any questions or come by for a test drive. Can't wait to see it go to a great new home!",
      "price": 29900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera is powered by the 3.6L M96 flat-six, utilizing VarioCam Plus for optimized valve timing and lift. Power is delivered to the rear wheels via a G96 6-speed manual transaxle with a crisp, short-throw linkage. The mechanical provenance is bolstered by a documented IMS bearing ceramic retrofit and a recent RMS replacement. The suspension geometry is dialed in with refreshed control arms and Bilstein B6 dampers, maintaining excellent lateral stability. While the exterior shows honest patina from spirited use, the drivetrain remains tight with no signs of bore scoring or AOS failure. A mechanically sound enthusiast build optimized for peak power-to-weight performance.",
      "price": 34500.0,
